        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post $2150 A month for a great apartment Each apartment has its own HVAC heating and air conditioning system. Has own hot water tank. Granite countertops countertops Stainless steel appliances Big beautiful shower. Much cabinet space in bathroom All modern kitchens and bath Low utility bills. Never go outside heated In building Free laundry room. Newly renovated, beautiful apartment 1 bedrooms has an ensuite full bathroom. Great natural light. Plenty of free street parking on Ohio, Armour and Ashland. Dog park right there. Nice friendly neighborhood. Close to trains, buses, expressways. Near Mariano's Walking distance to great restaurants, brewery, parks, festivals, Fulton, Randolph, Chicago ave. Pet friendly. Also have limited assigned parking for $150 extra Big beautiful back yard too. Rare to have all these things in one spot. Call Allie to see it. 3123750118 West Town 2 bedroom 2 bath Very efficient $600 MOVE IN FEE NONREFUNDABLE $250 PET FEE NONREFUNDABLE PROCESSING FEE $49 EACH NONREFUNDABLE Free Washer and Dryer in building Must do on line credit, background and verification check. Available JULY 15TH AND August 1ST Call ALLIE OR CEASAR 312-375-0118 We reserve the right to correct post's errors before, after and during post if there are any.",
