        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Call Apartment Guys at 773-549-3474 and ask for reference #1024550. Large rehabbed Gold Coast one bed on quiet tree lined street! This apartment features large floor-to-ceiling windows that let in lots of sunlight, plentiful closet space, a spacious floor plan and an updated kitchen with a dishwasher. Building amenities include a 24hr door staff, roof deck, outdoor pool, fitness center and extra storage lockers. Located in the heart of the Gold Coast, within walking distance to the lake, shops, restaurants, nightlife, bus lines and the EL. Prices are subject to change. ***Photos may be of a similar unit.****For faster response best to call or text 773-549-3474 with reference #1024550",
