        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 1-Bedroom Apartment in PRIME Lakeview East. OPTIONAL FULLY FURNISHED! Available: August or September, flexible on timing! Rent: $2,490/month I'm looking for a subletter to take over my lease, which ends May 30, 2027, with the option to extend. Spacious, sunny 8th-floor corner unit in a well-maintained elevator building with excellent management. Great amount of space - for your work-from-home setup, a couple living together, and hosting friends. Southwest facing with tons of natural light all day long, and beautiful sunset views. I've loved living here for over a year now and am only moving because I'm moving in with a partner. Features include: * Recently updated kitchen and bathroom * Stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher *Microwave * Brand new window AC units in both the living room and bedroom (installed less than a year ago) that work great Building Amenities * Rooftop deck * Laundry room (credit card payment accepted) * Bike room * Storage space * Garage parking available for an additional fee PRIME LOCATION: Quiet, tree-lined street near Wellington & Sheridan. * Steps from the Lakefront Trail. One block from Lincoln Park. * Walking distance to coffee shops, restaurants, bus stops, and the express bus downtown *Two blocks from Mariano's OPTIONAL FULLY FURNISHED: * Large sectional couch * Queen-sized bed * Mattress * Nightstands * Dresser * Kitchen island * Solid oak dining table * Restoration Hardware dining chairs * TV Furniture is optional and comes with the unit free of charge! Looking for someone to take over my lease, ending 5/30/2027 with option to extend",
