        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PLEASE READ: CALL OR TEXT DANIEL (314-278-8987) @ THE APARTMENT SOURCE CHICAGO FOR A TOUR OR MORE INFO. Please DO NOT reply directly on Craigslist, CALL/TEXT instead. PLEASE SPECIFY the ad you are inquiring about. Rental Requirements: * 650 Credit (can have a co-signer if between 580-650) co-signer must have 700 credit and 5x the rent with income * Monthly household income (combined between multiple tenants) must be at least 3x the rental price * No evictions, bankruptcies, or major collections within the past 7 years Located at the corner of 26th Street and Central Park Avenue, this beautifully renovated unit is ready for immediate move-in. Enjoy brand new finishes and spacious design in the heart of the Little Village neighborhood. Features: • Bright and open-concept living room with large windows • Brand new kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, white oak cabinets, dishwasher, and microwave • Modern bathrooms with marble tile and deep soaking tub • Three full-size bedrooms with windows, ceiling fans, and deep closet space Additional features include brand new hardwood flooring throughout, in-unit laundry, central air and central heat, and high-efficiency lighting. Additional Information: Street parking available. Pets under 60 lbs allowed (other than Pitbulls). Available now. Contact today to schedule a showing. This one won’t last long.",
