        "geocode_query": "6528 Nebraska Ave near 165th",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Charming one bedroom for rent in Hassville, IN. First floor. Central cooling and heating. Nice size front room and dining room. A lot of light. Hot and cold water, garbage, grass care, and maintanance is included. Tenant pays reasonable NIPSCO bill. Credit and backgrund check. No pets due to alergies. No smoking No vouchers. Leave a message if calling. Near I -80 / I - 65. Close to Perdue College in Hammond - 5 minute drive. It is 30 minutes drive to Chicago and Indiana Dunes. Near elementary and high school. Train Station East Chicago and new sport complex is 8 minutes drive.",
