        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PROPERTY INFO Rent: $4,918 / Month (rent only) Beds: 3 Bath: 2 Pet: Pet Friendly When is your Move-In Date? THIS UNIT WILL RENT FASTER THAN FREE DONUTS IN A BREAK ROOM. Text or Call Dave at 773.999.6670 to book a tour or for more details. PHOTOS ARE OF SIMILAR UNIT. FEATURES Balcony-None Central Air-Yes Dishwasher-All Dogs-No Weight Limit EV Charging Fitness Center Flooring-Hardwood Only Garage Laundry- W/D In Unit Luxury Property Security-Intercom/Key Fob Smoking-No Stove-Gas This spacious three-bedroom, two-bath apartment features an open layout with exposed concrete ceilings, wood plank flooring, and a modern kitchen with an island, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an in-unit washer and dryer. Residents enjoy a fitness center, co-working lounge, rooftop deck with grills, entertainment room, dog run, and bike storage. Located in the heart of Lakeview, you're just steps from Gill Park and close to the lakefront, Wrigley Field, Whole Foods, and countless restaurants, shops, and nightlife. Dave Sheehan 773-999-6670 Hotspot Rentals, LLC (License #481.011892) Our brokerage provides tenant introductions and representation to renters as part of the leasing process. We do not charge or collect any fees from tenants and do not handle lease transactions directly. Compensation is received from landlords or property management companies for brokerage services upon successful lease execution. Hotspot Apartment Rentals LLC — Illinois Licensed Real Estate Brokerage (#481.011892), Designated Managing Broker: Dorothy Moody (#471.006436), Virtual Office License Number 495.000153. Office of Record (mailing address only): One North Franklin Street, Suite 1200 Chicago IL 60606, Phone: (312) 782-8404 This website constitutes the virtual office of Hotspot Apartment Rentals LLC as authorized by the Illinois Department of Financial and Professional Regulation (IDFPR) under 225 ILCS 454/5-45(d). Disclaimer: PRICING COULD BE NET E