        "mainpic": "0c402194-5ebb-494e-b8b8-9cacad484952",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 2 Bed / 2 Bath with spacious open-plan living room and kitchen, located at Pratt and Ashland Blvd. This beautiful first-floor apartment in Rogers Park features a large living space suitable for both dining and living room areas, two large bedrooms (one with a half-wall built-in bookshelf), a master bath with functional jets in the tub and another bathroom with a shower. The apartment is 1,100 sq. ft. and includes a storage unit in the basement, along with easy access to the alley out back. Each bedroom includes plenty of closet space. Conveniently located a 5 minute walk from the Morse Red Line station and Morse Fresh market grocery, or 5 minutes in the other direction to Clark street and numerous delicious restaurants, and a 15 minute walk from the beach. Start date: Aug 1 Rent: $1,950 per month Features: ⁃ In-unit washer and dryer ⁃ Central AC and heating ⁃ 2 full bathrooms! ⁃ Dishwasher ⁃ Microwave ⁃ Built in bookcase ⁃ Basement storage unit ⁃ Pets allowed ⁃ Beautiful front courtyard",
