        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PROPERTY INFO ID: 317307844 Rent: $2,330 / Month (rent only) Beds: 1 Bath: 1 Pet: Pet Friendly When is your Move-In Date? Text or Call Dave at 773.999.6670 to book a tour or for more details. PHOTOS ARE OF SIMILAR UNIT. Pricing and availability are subject to change daily, and I specialize in helping serious renters find the best option quickly - if you're ready to move, I’ll take great care of you. FEATURES Balcony-Some Units Central Air-Yes Dishwasher-All Dogs-No Weight Limit Fitness Center Flooring-Hardwood Only Garage High-Rise Laundry- W/D In Unit Luxury Property New Property Security-24 Hour Doorman Smoking-No Stove-Gas PROPERTY HIGHLIGHTS • Efficient 1-bedroom layout with great separation of space • Approximately 600 square feet • High ceilings with exposed concrete for a modern loft feel • Floor-to-ceiling windows with roller shades • Wood plank flooring throughout • European-style kitchen with soft-close cabinetry • White quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances • Under-cabinet lighting • In-unit washer and dryer • Smart thermostat and keyless entry • Full luxury amenity package • Rooftop terrace with zen garden and fire features • Multiple seating and lounge areas • Fitness center • Demonstration kitchen • Library and game room • Prime South Loop location • Near Museum Campus and lakefront trails • Walk Score of 95 • Steps to Roosevelt CTA (Red, Green, Orange Lines) • Easy access to multiple bus routes and Divvy station • Pet-friendly community • Dog run and pet wash station • Cats and dogs welcome (breed restrictions apply) • Garage parking available for an additional monthly fee Dave Sheehan 773.999.6670 Hotspot Rentals, LLC (License #481.011892) Our brokerage provides tenant introductions and representation to renters as part of the leasing process. We do not charge or collect any fees from tenants and do not handle lease transactions directly. Compensation is received from landlords or property management companies for brokerage services upon successful lease execution. Hotspot Apartment Rentals LLC — Illinois Licensed Real Estate Brokerage (#481.011892), Designated Managing Broker: Dorothy Moody (#471.006436), Virtual Office License Number 495.000153. Office of Record (mailing address only): One North Franklin Street, Suite 1200 Chicago IL 60606, Phone: (312) 782-8404 This website constitutes the virtual office of Hotspot Apartment Rentals LLC as authorized by the Illinois Department of Financial and Professional Regulation (IDFPR) under 225 ILCS 454/5-45(d). Disclaimer: PRICING COULD BE NET EFFECTIVE OF SPECIALS, please ask if there is one. Photos may not be of exact unit available and may be of various model units and various vacant units. Apartment availability and lease terms may vary. Pricing, availability, and specials are subject to change at any time and without notice. Please note that the price may be net effective of a special or concession that the building is currently running. Information is believed to be accurate, however, is subject to errors and omissions. HotSpot Rentals services the following neighborhoods: South Loop, Printers Row, Near North, River North, Gold Coast, West Loop, Fulton River District, West Loop Gate, The Loop, Streeterville, Lakeshore East, New East Side, Old Town, Medical District, University Village, Near North, River West, Lincoln Park South, Lakeview, Uptown, Ukrainian Village, Wicker Park, Edgewater, Ravenswood, Bronzeville, Logan Square.",
