        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Description Newly renovated spacious 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment available in Hyde Park/Kenwood - Boulevard Address. Apartment includes: Great natural light, hardwood flooring throughout, French doors off the living room, stainless steel appliances including microwave, great closet space, doorbells with intercoms. Rent: $1,500 - heat and water included in the rent Vintage, well manicured building with on-site management, security cameras, laundry facility, and bike room. Off-street parking lot located to the north of the building with assigned parking for extra monthly fee, while spots available. 5 minutes from the University of Chicago; 10 minutes from the Loop Excellent public transportation, short distance to Lake Shore Drive. Both University of Chicago Police and CPD service area. Rent: $1,500 - heat and water included in the rent Call Redel Rentals at (773) 819-9216 to schedule a viewing appointment For more information, visit - https://www.redelrentals.com/buildings/43rd-drexel-blvd 4336-44 S. Drexel Blvd. property accommodates residents looking for studio, one, and two bedroom apartments. On-site management with nearly 50 years experience; office is located in the main building at 43rd and Drexel. - Beautifully manicured courtyard building with 24-hour security surveillance cameras, on-site laundry facility, bike room, and assigned parking on lot to north of building. - Property is walking distance from parks, cafes, as well as burgeoning retail shops and restaurants, like Bronzeville Winery. Lakefront access is a 10 min walk from the 43rd St. Pedestrian Bridge; 20 min walk to Oakwood Beach. - Less than 2 miles from University of Chicago (to the south); less than 2 miles from IIT (to the northwest); less than 4.5 miles from University of Illinois - Chicago (to the northwest); less than 4.5 miles from Columbia College (to the north). - CTA's #43 bus stop is located at 43rd St. and Drexel Blvd. and the #4 bus stop is conveniently located right around the corner at 43rd St. and Cottage Grove Ave. The CTA \"L\" Green line train is also within close proximity. Call 773-819-9216 for more information! Features Hardwood floors Refrigerator Walk-in closets Stove and oven Heat Ceiling fan Controlled access Courtyard Mirrors View Window coverings Cat friendly Laundry room Parking Lake access On-site management Recycling",
