        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Stunning Luxury High-Rise Living on Michigan Avenue | Unbeatable Grant Park & Lake Views | Studios to 4BR Penthouses Rise above it all in one of downtown Chicago's most talked-about new luxury towers, perched on iconic South Michigan Avenue directly across from Grant Park. Designed by a world-renowned architect with interiors by a celebrated Chicago designer, this striking glass high-rise offers completely unobstructed views of Lake Michigan, Grant Park, Millennium Park, and the downtown skyline from floor-to-ceiling windows in every home. Choose from thoughtfully designed studios and convertibles, one-bedrooms (some with dens), spacious two- and three-bedrooms, and jaw-dropping four-bedroom penthouses with 360° panoramas. Every residence features designer kitchens, premium fixtures, elevated finishes, and abundant natural light. Select studios include custom floor-to-ceiling bookshelf dividers and built-in desks — perfect for remote work. You're steps from the Loop, the lakefront trail, Museum Campus, Millennium Park, world-class dining, and the Cultural Mile. This is the rare address that delivers big-city energy and a private, elevated retreat all at once. Features & Amenities 80,000+ sq ft of indoor and outdoor amenity space — among the largest in downtown Chicago Private 73rd-floor rooftop observation deck — the highest residential vantage point in the city Wintergarden with year-round swimming Two-story state-of-the-art fitness and wellness center overlooking the park and lake Floor-to-ceiling windows with lake, park, and skyline views Designer kitchens and premium finish packages in every unit Studio, convertible, 1BR, 1BR+den, 2BR, 3BR, and 4BR penthouse floor plans Beautiful Co-working Spaces Pet friendly Professional on-site management MOVE IN SPECIAL: up to 1 month free on select apartments* Why Work With Us? This listing is brought to you by LoopLuxuryLiving.com — Chicago's free, concierge-style luxury apartment locating service. We specialize exclusively in downtown's premier neighborhoods: the Loop, South Loop, Fulton Market, and Streeterville. Our service costs you absolutely nothing — we're compensated by the buildings, not by you. We'll match you with the perfect luxury residence, schedule your tours, and guide you through the entire leasing process from first showing to signed lease. Call or text regarding this property!! Chris 815-277-9239 License Number: 475.218048 *Please Note: Listed rents may be net effective of current building specials — ask us what's running now! Photos may show model or comparable units rather than the exact available apartment. Pricing, availability, lease terms, and promotions are set by the property and can change without notice. The information is believed to be accurate but is subject to errors and omissions. Contact LoopLuxuryLiving.com or text me (815-277-9239) to verify current details and schedule your free tour.",
