        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post AVAILABLE Sept 2 -- if this ad is still up, please contact us. Fantastic, FULLY FURNISHED, beautiful, 1 bed, den, 1.5 baths, with great views, doorman building, $2445 (parking available for additional monthly fee, if you need it) Rare opportunity to move into turn-key fully furnished and equipped condo apartment, move-in immaculate condition person looking for downtown Chicago apartment. Modern, high rise condo building, complete amenities, $2,445/month includes most utilities (high-speed internet and cable). Tenant(s) responsible for electric. Apartment: Fully furnished in all rooms, move-in condition. Spacious 1077 sf Move in ready with complete kitchen equipment and bed/bath supplies High floor with stunning city views Large terrace (spectacular 4th of July viewing) Wood floors in living areas (except carpet in BR) Open kitchen, granite counters, dishwasher, gas stove/oven, dishes/silverware/pots & pans Washer/Dryer in Unit Guest half-bathroom/powder room Master bedroom with private en suite bathroom Private den/office/guest room with french doors for privacy Workout and weight room on premises Large pool and sundeck Business office on premises For hygiene and public health purposes, you would have to provide your own linens & towels Location: * Centrally located near (Roosevelt \"L\" CTA train stop for Red, Orange and Green lines) for easy travel to Midway, O'Hare, U of Chicago, suburbs and of course downtown and inner city areas * 1 block off Michigan Avenue * If you run or hike, you are one block from the park/lake trails -- run or bike along Lake Michigan/Grant Park * Short walk to downtown business district, Lake Michigan, Soldier Field, Field museum, Aquarium, Planetarium, Chicago Institute of Art * Very near/walk to: Trader Joes, Whole Foods, Osco, Target, Starbucks, Walgreens, Home Depot, Best Buy & more * Fantastic restaurants within steps (too many to count) Lease requirement: Minimum 12 months (through August 31, 2026). Tenant(s) suitability: This unit is in top shape. NO pets, smokers or illegal drug use, and NO AirBnB, subleasing, or assignment of lease. Please respond by email with: 1) Your name(s) 2) Phone and email contact information where we can reach you 3) Current address 4) Current living situation (and why you'd like to move to this apartment?) 5) Any other information that you'd like to share about yourself (we told you a lot about this unit, so we'd like to hear about you) Please note that because our rent of $2,445 includes beautiful furnishings, our price can't be compared to other rentals for unfurnished apartments. For this location, size of apartment, outdoor views and more, you can't beat this! And if you have a car, parking in the building garage (accessible by the building elevator) is available as stated above for an added amount.",
