        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Check out our 1 bed/1 bath Lincoln Park unit! This south-facing fourth floor unit features PLENTY of closet space, stainless steel appliances, a one-minute walk from the Fullerton Red/Brown/Purple CTA station, and new in-unit washer and dryer. Water and heating/cooking gas are provided by the HOA and are included in the tenant's rent. Tenant will be responsible for their electricity and WiFi/Cable. Pets are allowed, with restrictions. The building has Parcel Pending lockers for your delivery packages, a Butterfly system for secure entry into the building, a storage room with your own storage locker, and a bike room. This is an elevator building! Available for a August 1st move-in. Tours to be scheduled the week of July 6th. Additional information: - There is NO security deposit. Non-refundable move-in fee is $700, non-refundable move-out fee is $700. Tenant is responsible for HOA moving fees. - Tenant will have to pay first month's rent, move-in fee, and associated HOA moving fees within 72 business hours of an executed lease. - Tenant will need to provide proof of renter's insurance. - Please inquire for an application if you are interested. Applications are about $75 and paid directly to the service used (we receive no income from this process).",
